  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our research involves the detailed description of the content of the diet of x dialysis
      patients.

      For our purpose we used a newly developed &quot;food frequency questionnaire&quot;. This is the first
      validated questionnaire specific for dialysis patients and we were the first to use it.

      Our special focus was the fiber content in the diet of our patient. Our thesis that they are
      way below the recommended guidelines for fiber intake was verified. Our follow will evaluate
      the effect of such at diet, mosTLy cardiovascular.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
